Package battleship

Class EmptySea

java.lang.Object
battleship.Ship
battleship.EmptySea
public class EmptySea
extends Ship
Empty Sea is a class that is derived from Ship EmptySea serves a "catch-all" ship filling in the spaces in the game board array where there is no ship. The effect is every location in the array has a "ship". The ship will be an actual ship or a EmptySea.
